    <item>
      <title>英国经济：通胀放缓，降息希望增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/uk-economy-inflation-slows-boosting-rate-cut-hopes-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国 12 月份通胀率三个月来首次意外回落，这让人们对英国央行下个月降息的希望不减。彭博社的 Lizzy Burden 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/uk-economy-inflation-slows-boosting-rate-cut-hopes-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 07:44:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国制裁后俄罗斯原油在中国沿海堆积如山</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/more-russian-oil-stranded-off-chinese-coast-after-us-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于贸易商、炼油商和航运公司试图避免受到美国针对俄罗斯能源流动实施的史上最严厉制裁的影响，中国沿海滞留的石油数量正在不断增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/more-russian-oil-stranded-off-chinese-coast-after-us-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 07:42:26 GMT</pubDate>
