    <item>
      <title>英国通胀放缓后，交易员加大对英国央行降息的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示英国12月份通胀率意外下降，缓解了人们对持续价格压力的担忧，货币市场纷纷预期英国央行今年将进一步降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 07:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴罗佐：欧盟应继续与中国进行贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/barroso-eu-should-continue-to-trade-with-china-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前欧盟委员会主席、高盛国际顾问公司主席若泽·曼努埃尔·巴罗佐认为，如果欧盟停止与中国的贸易，将对欧洲、中国乃至世界经济造成损害。他在高盛 2025 年亚太全球宏观会议间隙与 Minmin Low 和 Haslinda Amin 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/barroso-eu-should-continue-to-trade-with-china-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:01:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>面对交易员削减押注，欧洲央行仍捍卫降息路径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/ecb-defends-rate-cutting-path-in-face-of-traders-paring-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行正在反驳那些认为通胀走强、美国就业市场意外强劲以及唐纳德·特朗普的经济混乱将缩小降息空间的投资者的观点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/ecb-defends-rate-cutting-path-in-face-of-traders-paring-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国因强迫劳动指控禁止进口 37 家中国公司产品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/us-bans-imports-from-37-china-firms-due-to-alleged-forced-labor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府已将中国采矿、太阳能和纺织行业的 37 家公司列入禁止向美国出口的名单，原因是涉嫌在新疆地区存在强迫劳动行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/us-bans-imports-from-37-china-firms-due-to-alleged-forced-labor</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 02:43:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟可能对俄罗斯实施禁令，中国供应趋势推动铝价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/aluminum-rises-on-eu-s-possible-russia-ban-china-supply-trends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铝价小幅上涨，欧盟考虑对俄罗斯金属实施进口限制，且中国产量增长预计将放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/aluminum-rises-on-eu-s-possible-russia-ban-china-supply-trends</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 02:39:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
